    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>capers</strong> roughly</p><p>Chop your <strong>black</strong> <strong>olives</strong> in half</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>paste</strong> in 500ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[650ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1L] </span><strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>stock</strong></p>",
