          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the orzo is almost cooked, add your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> to the pan and cook, covered, for a further 5 min or until the basa is cooked through and the orzo is tender – this is your <strong>basa puttanesca orzo</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
